Waxman Industries Inc said it filedwith the Securities and Exchange Commission a registrationstatement covering a 25 mln dlr issue of convertiblesubordinated debentures due 2007.    Proceeds will be used to repay short-term indebtedness andfor general corporate purposes, which may include acquisitions,Waxman said.    The company named Drexel Burnham Lambert Inc as soleunderwriter of the offering. Reuter&#3;